[A map of the distribution of malaria in Venezuela is found in the 2014 World Malaria Report (http://www.who.int/malaria/publications/world_malaria_report_2014/wmr-2014-profiles.pdf), on page 161. 35 per cent are _P. falciparum_ and 65 per cent _P. vivax_. The number of registered cases has slowly but steadily increased since 2008, although mortality has continued to decrease. - Mod.EP

